&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>This code is safe, perfectly fine. But it&amp;rsquo;s not clean. The core intent is buried under layers of validation. What if&amp;hellip; we could flip this pattern on its head?&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Approaches to replicate Unreal Engine's TMap</title><link>https://rezonated.github.io/posts/tmap_replication/</link><pubDate>Sat, 14 Jun 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://rezonated.github.io/posts/tmap_replication/</guid><description>&lt;h1 class="heading" id="introduction">
