&lt;h1 class="heading" id="why-cant-tmap-be-replicated-by-unreal">
 Why can&amp;rsquo;t TMap be replicated by Unreal?
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#why-cant-tmap-be-replicated-by-unreal">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>Unreal&amp;rsquo;s built-in replication only supports certain types that the replication system knows how to serialize. This includes basic primitives, some containers like &lt;code>TArray&lt;/code>, &lt;code>FVector&lt;/code>, or custom structs containing &lt;code>UPROPERTY&lt;/code> fields.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>